WEBVTT

00:00:01.076 --> 00:00:02.636
Hello, everyone.

00:00:03.196 --> 00:00:05.236
My name is Orit, yes.

00:00:05.916 --> 00:00:08.916
And I study insurance.

00:00:09.716 --> 00:00:14.556
Telling people that you study insurance
is not a good way to start a conversation.

00:00:15.276 --> 00:00:18.876
In fact, if ever you need
to end the conversation,

00:00:18.916 --> 00:00:21.796
try it, tell people you study insurance.

00:00:22.476 --> 00:00:24.476
People don't want to talk about insurance.

00:00:24.516 --> 00:00:26.556
They don't think it's all that exciting.

00:00:26.916 --> 00:00:28.276
But I disagree.

00:00:29.076 --> 00:00:33.156
I find insurance fascinating;
in fact, I find it magical.